# 🧠 Backend Clean Architecture – Node.js + Express + TypeScript

Project ini dibuat menggunakan **Node.js**, **Express**, dan **TypeScript** dengan penerapan konsep **Clean Architecture** agar struktur kode lebih modular, mudah di-maintain, dan scalable.

---

## 📂 Project Structure

├── config/ # Konfigurasi database, environment, dan koneksi
├── domain/ # Entity / model bisnis utama
├── infrastructure/ # Akses ke data (repository, query SQL, dll)
├── interfaces/ # Layer interface (controller, route, response handler)
├── middlewares/ # Middleware (auth JWT, validator, dsb)
├── types/ # TypeScript type definitions
├── usecases/ # Business logic utama (interaksi domain & repository)
├── utils/ # Helper / fungsi umum
└── index.ts # Entry point utama aplikasi


---

## 🚀 How to Run the Project

### 1️⃣ Clone Repository

git clone https://github.com/username/nama-project.git
cd nama-project

### 2️⃣ Install Dependencies
npm install

### 3️⃣ Setup Environment Variables
ubah file .env-example.txt menjadi .env

🧩 Run Modes
🔹 Development Mode
npm run dev

🔹 Build Project (Compile TypeScript)
npm run build

🔹 Run Production Build
npm start
